                <p class="text-justify">According to experts, tourists must start their ticket search around 64 days from the intended day of departure to avoid huge traffic while booking a Flight. The prices of flights not only depend on the time of day, the day, and the month, and whether the flight being booked is domestic or international. The important question is, "how far in advance should I book a flight 2023?”. Following answers their questions: </p>

